7
00:00:38,479 --> 00:00:40,516
{\an1}Then let's all four
of us join forces now!

8
00:00:40,550 --> 00:00:42,153
{\an1}"All four of us?"

9
00:00:42,187 --> 00:00:44,958
{\an1}You treat us like
we're human, too!

10
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:47,563
What kind of
childrearing led to this?!

11
00:00:47,596 --> 00:00:49,000
[chuckling]

12
