00:01:00,554 --> 00:01:02,191
{\an1}Plus, I already know!

17
00:01:07,167 --> 00:01:08,102
I...

18
00:01:09,104 --> 00:01:11,742
I already met
Mom's chakra, dad.

19
00:01:12,878 --> 00:01:14,782
{\an1}What you want to say
to me is the same as

20
00:01:14,815 --> 00:01:16,919
{\an1}my talkative mom, right?

21
00:01:16,952 --> 00:01:18,588
{\an1}See, I already know!

22
00:01:20,025 --> 00:01:21,462
[chuckle]

23
00:01:37,559 --> 00:01:38,861
This feeling...

24
00:01:39,161 --> 00:01:40,630
{\an1}It's so familiar.

25
00:01:42,601 --> 00:01:45,005
{\an1}Even though we have few
options, it feels like we

26
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:47,009
{\an1}can accomplish anything.

27
00:01:49,314 --> 00:01:50,716
That's right!

28
00:01:50,749 --> 00:01:54,224
{\an1}This feels just like
when I was with Kushina.

29
00:02:05,010 --> 00:02:06,881
I feel power
welling up inside me!

30
00:02:07,549 --> 00:02:09,018
{\an1}Come on, let's go!

31
00:02:10,787 --> 00:02:12,558
Naruto's got
this much chakra?

32
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,529
Naruto!

33
00:02:14,829 --> 00:02:17,434
{\an1}Shouting and showing off is
all well and good but don't

34
00:02:17,468 --> 00:02:21,375
{\an1}tell me you've forgotten
that nothing other than Sage

35
00:02:21,408 --> 00:02:23,846
{\an1}Jutsu is going to
work against this guy!

36
00:02:24,514 --> 00:02:26,150
{\an1}I know you're not an idiot!

37
00:02:36,836 --> 00:02:38,173
That's right!

38
00:02:39,242 --> 00:02:40,311
Okay...

39
00:02:40,344 --> 00:02:42,113
{\an1}You're a bigger idiot
than my elder brother!

40
00:02:42,147 --> 00:02:45,554
{\an1}All that Chakra and
it's being wasted on him.

41
00:02:45,588 --> 00:02:48,859
Or perhaps not
quite the same feeling.

42
00:02:50,028 --> 00:02:51,665
[laughter]

43
00:02:52,667 --> 00:02:56,274
{\an1}You've sure surpassed
all the previous Hokage!

44
00:02:56,307 --> 00:02:58,078
{\an1}'Least, in stupidity!

45
00:02:58,111 --> 00:02:59,880
Shut up!

46
00:03:00,215 --> 00:03:01,818
Stupid Kurama!

47
00:03:02,151 --> 00:03:03,588
[laughter]

48
00:03:03,622 --> 00:03:06,760
{\an1}Fools are easily liked
and trusted by others.

49
00:03:06,793 --> 00:03:08,732
{\an1}But don't you mind that.

50
00:03:08,764 --> 00:03:10,701
{\an1}There's no need to worry.

51
00:03:10,736 --> 00:03:13,674
{\an1}I'm not worried that
I'm an idiot, you know!

52
00:03:13,707 --> 00:03:14,976
Not at all!

53
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:16,445
No, not that.

54
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:17,615
Huh?

55
00:03:17,649 --> 00:03:20,887
{\an1}I'm saying that you might
be able to go into Sage Mode

56
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:23,225
{\an1}while in Tailed Beast State.

57
00:03:23,258 --> 00:03:24,695
[gasp]

58
